PATROCLUS, [to Thersites, who is playing Ajax]  Jove
bless great Ajax.

THERSITES  Hum!

PATROCLUS  I come from the worthy Achilles--

THERSITES  Ha?

PATROCLUS  Who most humbly desires you to invite
Hector to his tent--

THERSITES  Hu